[mypy-boto3-builder](https://github.com/youtype/mypy_boto3_builder) carefully generates type annotations for each service, patiently waiting for `aiobotocore` updates. it delivers drop-in type This package provides type annotations for the aiobotocore.VoiceID service, compatible with various IDEs and tools like VSCode, PyCharm, and mypy, to facilitate code completion and bug detection. It's generated with mypy-boto3-builder 7.23.2 and requires Python version 3.8 or higher.
